# Inter-Observer Agreement

**AI assistance improved consistency between radiologists**

| Metric | Control | AI-Assisted | Improvement |
|--------|---------|-------------|-------------|
| **Kappa Coefficient** | 0.73 | 0.84 | +15.1% |
| **Sensitivity Agreement** | 78.2% | 89.6% | +11.4% |
| **Specificity Agreement** | 82.1% | 91.3% | +9.2% |
| **Management Agreement** | 75.8% | 86.7% | +10.9% |

**Reduced variability leads to more consistent patient care**

@notes:
- Kappa >0.8 indicates excellent agreement
- Sensitivity agreement crucial for cancer cases
- Management agreement includes follow-up recommendations
- Consistency improves quality of care across providers

---

